aims for his torso and fires multiple shots. 


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, TrikeJacob@n... wrote:
> Triceradon shoves his way past Mosquitor and heads toward the 
bridge of the ship. Ultracon follows right behind him. They fire 
their guns at any predacon they see along the way.
> 
> Meanwhile, outside the base, Stegotron is ducking and dodging the 
autogun fire. "man" he thought, "these predacons have bad aim." Then 
he sees Triceradon and Ultracon have made it inside the Predacon 
base, so he calls Dinotron and goes in after them.
